Package: clinconcept
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Loading and Querying Clinical Concept Dictionaries in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Rob", "Free", , "rcfree@protonmail.com", c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8053-435X"))
  )
Maintainer: Rob Free <rcfree@protonmail.com>
Description: Tools to work with clinical concept dictionaries by enabling researchers to build local or remote databases
  using UK National Health Service (NHS) based concept dictionary downloads and then query terms/concepts directly or through hierarchical/graphs-based relationships.
  Supported by this tool are NHS-based downloads of READ versions 2 and 3, SNOMED-CT and ICD10.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
